{"id": "kansen-en-uitdagingen-in-het-vastgoed__a2-late-chunking__0002", "text": "[Claire van Staaij](https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/authors/claire-van-staaij/index.html)", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "kansen-en-uitdagingen-in-het-vastgoed__a2-late-chunking__0002", "source_slug": "kansen-en-uitdagingen-in-het-vastgoed", "source_title": "Opportunities and challenges in real estate", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/sectoren-en-trends/real-estate/kansen-en-uitdagingen-in-het-vastgoed.html", "source_date": "2025-05-01", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "real estate", "topic": "sectoren en trends", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 2, "n_chunks_total": 16, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 2}}
{"id": "kansen-en-uitdagingen-in-het-vastgoed__a2-late-chunking__0003", "text": "In the podcast De Steen, Wouter Truffino speaks with experts about current themes within the construction and real estate sector. Social and political developments are discussed and knowledge and experiences are shared to solve relevant issues. From the housing construction challenge to the energy transition, from biodiversity to climate change.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "kansen-en-uitdagingen-in-het-vastgoed__a2-late-chunking__0003", "source_slug": "kansen-en-uitdagingen-in-het-vastgoed", "source_title": "Opportunities and challenges in real estate", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/sectoren-en-trends/real-estate/kansen-en-uitdagingen-in-het-vastgoed.html", "source_date": "2025-05-01", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "real estate", "topic": "sectoren en trends", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 3, "n_chunks_total": 16, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 3}}
{"id": "kansen-en-uitdagingen-in-het-vastgoed__a2-late-chunking__0004", "text": "Real Estate Sector Banker Claire van Staaij from ABN AMRO shares her vision on market developments in this podcast. The obligation of a minimum energy label C ensures more energy-efficient buildings in the office market. There is now a division in this market. Building owners must continue to invest in making their office real estate more sustainable, especially now that users are increasingly focusing on sustainability.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "kansen-en-uitdagingen-in-het-vastgoed__a2-late-chunking__0004", "source_slug": "kansen-en-uitdagingen-in-het-vastgoed", "source_title": "Opportunities and challenges in real estate", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/sectoren-en-trends/real-estate/kansen-en-uitdagingen-in-het-vastgoed.html", "source_date": "2025-05-01", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "real estate", "topic": "sectoren en trends", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 4, "n_chunks_total": 16, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 4}}
{"id": "kansen-en-uitdagingen-in-het-vastgoed__a2-late-chunking__0005", "text": "Real estate investors active in rental properties have been facing headwinds for several years. Various tax changes and other measures aimed at protecting tenants are hitting investors in the pockets. This has been a reason for more and more investors to sell their rental properties and offer them on the owner-occupied market. That process accelerated in 2024. As a result, a rental property is no longer the investment object it was years ago.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "kansen-en-uitdagingen-in-het-vastgoed__a2-late-chunking__0005", "source_slug": "kansen-en-uitdagingen-in-het-vastgoed", "source_title": "Opportunities and challenges in real estate", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/sectoren-en-trends/real-estate/kansen-en-uitdagingen-in-het-vastgoed.html", "source_date": "2025-05-01", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "real estate", "topic": "sectoren en trends", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 5, "n_chunks_total": 16, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 5}}
{"id": "kansen-en-uitdagingen-in-het-vastgoed__a2-late-chunking__0006", "text": "## Listen to the De Steen podcast with Sector Banker Claire van Staaij", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "kansen-en-uitdagingen-in-het-vastgoed__a2-late-chunking__0006", "source_slug": "kansen-en-uitdagingen-in-het-vastgoed", "source_title": "Opportunities and challenges in real estate", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/sectoren-en-trends/real-estate/kansen-en-uitdagingen-in-het-vastgoed.html", "source_date": "2025-05-01", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "real estate", "topic": "sectoren en trends", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 6, "n_chunks_total": 16, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 6}}
{"id": "kansen-en-uitdagingen-in-het-vastgoed__a2-late-chunking__0007", "text": "Also read the publication '[More energy-efficient offices and shop vacancies, increase from ponds](https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/sectoren-en-trends/stand-van-sectoren/real-estate/meer-energieenergiee-kantoor-en-winkelleegstand-groei-uitponden.html)'. In the office market, the obligation of a minimum energy label C ensures more energy-efficient buildings. The retail sector is struggling with more vacancies due to the bankruptcies of large retailers. The effects of the measures to cool the commercial rental housing market are becoming visible. Many landlords are shifting homes to the owner-occupied segment.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "kansen-en-uitdagingen-in-het-vastgoed__a2-late-chunking__0007", "source_slug": "kansen-en-uitdagingen-in-het-vastgoed", "source_title": "Opportunities and challenges in real estate", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/sectoren-en-trends/real-estate/kansen-en-uitdagingen-in-het-vastgoed.html", "source_date": "2025-05-01", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "real estate", "topic": "sectoren en trends", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 7, "n_chunks_total": 16, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 7}}
{"id": "kansen-en-uitdagingen-in-het-vastgoed__a2-late-chunking__0008", "text": "Our experts and representatives will discuss current topics with entrepreneurs and others on various stages and platforms. They talk about matters such as sustainable entrepreneurship, circular economy, real estate and social impact. Follow the webinars, podcasts and interviews.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "kansen-en-uitdagingen-in-het-vastgoed__a2-late-chunking__0008", "source_slug": "kansen-en-uitdagingen-in-het-vastgoed", "source_title": "Opportunities and challenges in real estate", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/sectoren-en-trends/real-estate/kansen-en-uitdagingen-in-het-vastgoed.html", "source_date": "2025-05-01", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "real estate", "topic": "sectoren en trends", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 8, "n_chunks_total": 16, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 8}}
{"id": "kansen-en-uitdagingen-in-het-vastgoed__a2-late-chunking__0009", "text": "[Watch the videos or listen to the podcasts](https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/in-spraak/index.html)", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "kansen-en-uitdagingen-in-het-vastgoed__a2-late-chunking__0009", "source_slug": "kansen-en-uitdagingen-in-het-vastgoed", "source_title": "Opportunities and challenges in real estate", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/sectoren-en-trends/real-estate/kansen-en-uitdagingen-in-het-vastgoed.html", "source_date": "2025-05-01", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "real estate", "topic": "sectoren en trends", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 9, "n_chunks_total": 16, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 9}}
{"id": "kansen-en-uitdagingen-in-het-vastgoed__a2-late-chunking__0010", "text": "In recent times, the real estate sector has been dominated by write-downs as a result of the sharp rise in interest rates. However, the prospects for the sector are favorable, as the need for homes and commercial buildings remains high due to the tight market and strong economy.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "kansen-en-uitdagingen-in-het-vastgoed__a2-late-chunking__0010", "source_slug": "kansen-en-uitdagingen-in-het-vastgoed", "source_title": "Opportunities and challenges in real estate", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/sectoren-en-trends/real-estate/kansen-en-uitdagingen-in-het-vastgoed.html", "source_date": "2025-05-01", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "real estate", "topic": "sectoren en trends", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 10, "n_chunks_total": 16, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 10}}
